title: All about ME
name: All about ME
description:
A Map by Brandonm

Places that are important in my life

properties.name: 101 Coffee Shop
properties.description: Posted by Brandonm  6145 Franklin Avenue, Los Angeles, CA, 90028One of the best, coolest coffee shops in LA. This is where they filmed Swingers and it\'s still a good celebrity sighting place. I\'ve seen Jack Black, Johnny Knoxville, Kelly Osbourne, Elijah Wood and others. If you go you MUST have the Waffle Brownie Sunday. It\'s amazing.

properties.name: Akbar
properties.description: Posted by Brandonm4356 W Sunset Blvd, Los Angeles, CAGay/Bi-Sexual/Straight bar. Great jukebox up front. I liked it better before they added the big dance area in the back

properties.description: Posted by BrandonmYeah, there isn\'t much out here. But a few times as a kid we took family road trips from LA to my dad\'s family in San Antonio and Austin and once or twice all the way to Georgia.

properties.name: Home in LA
properties.description: Posted by Brandonm337 N Ogden, LA, CAAnother incredible location to live in Los Angeles. Nearby you have Melrose Strip, CBS, The Grove, Farmers Market, major and independent movie theaters, great shops and restaurants.

properties.name: Home in WeHo
properties.description: Posted by Brandonm949 N Kings Rd, LA, CAThis was my last apartment before moving to NY. WeHo is great because you can walk to most anything you\'d need and there are always people hanging out outside, jogging and walking their dogs

properties.description: Posted by BrandonmStretches from Fairfax to La Brea. Lots of independent shops where you can usually haggle a lower price as well as major chain shops.

properties.name: My Palm Springs House
properties.description: Posted by BrandonmWell, ok... Cathedral City. But this place was great. Fountain in the front yard, long driveway, 3-car garage, split-level home, pool, jacuzzi with waterfall, fireplace, outdoor patios. It was great.

properties.description: Posted by BrandonmAlthough the roommate situation wasn\'t too great, it was a nice area (Beverly Hills ADJACENT). But not too much to walk to.

properties.description: Posted by BrandonmMelrose West of Fairfax quickly became flooded with upscale shopping while I lived in the area. You can find stores like Fred Segal, Marc Jacobs, Puma, Antique Denim, Energie, Miu Miu, Miss Sixty, Giant Robot, Paul Frank and many more.

properties.name: Robertson Blvd
properties.description: Posted by BrandonmDesigner label shopping and celebrity sighting. You can always see someone at Ivy or paparazzi standing outside a store waiting for Paris Hilton or Lindsay Lohan.
